ofxTwitterStream - supersimple branch
=====================================
This is basically the a bare and very simple
to use version of ofxTwitterStream and much more
in the spirit of OF "keeping it simple". 

How to install - only tested on Mac, XCode 4, with latest of-git version (may 2011)
=========================================
- tested on Mac, XCode 4
- using latest openFrameworks from GitHub (may 2011)

1) create a new group in your project 
2) draw and drop the "src" directory into this group

That's it!

